ecommBot_v0.1

An Agentic AI workflow model that takes chat input from user, show cases the available product options and value for the user, on further agreement calcualtes the cost and makes a deal.

Feature: Takes input for product requirement of user and returns the max discount avaialble on a the threshold order quantity after agreement.

Status: DEMO
NEXT UPDATE: plan of an additional feature of sending an email with the agreement and Invoice


